; Coverage for history.cc: price inversion in multi-step path
; A->B direct price, C->B direct price
; Converting A->C requires: A->B (direct) then B->C (inverted C->B)
; 10 A * 2 B/A / (5 B/C) = 4 C

P 2024/01/01 A 2 B
P 2024/01/01 C 5 B

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Test    10 A
    Assets:Cash

test bal --market --exchange C --now 2024/02/01 Expenses
                  C4  Expenses:Test
end test
